VALUES ('maths', 'Which property applies to the Error Function regarding its symmetry?', '["It is an even function: $\\text{erf}(-x) = \\text{erf}(x)$", "It is an odd function: $\\text{erf}(-x) = -\\text{erf}(x)$", "It is a periodic function", "It is a nowhere continuous function"]', 1);

